Specific topics are organized as â€œExamplesâ€ along the text or â€œApplicationsâ€ in the end of the chapter. These can be eventually skipped, but the reader is invited to stop just reading and explore these topics using a computer.

Understand that complex exponentials are eigenfunctions of LTI systems


